Morningcrest is a fortress in [[Thrane]] near the [[Aundair]] border. It is one of the three largest [[templar]] monasteries in [[Khorvaire]]. Here, templars of the [[Silver Flame]] live an austere life, dedicating themselves to combat training and religious studies.
